                        <item xml:id="a4">
                           <locus target="#00" n="#"> Fol. 136v: Sǝfrä säˁat "Measuring of the Hours".</locus>
                           <q xml:lang="gez"/>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- Short title of the book and crudely written notes (writing exercises): fol. 1r.&#xD;
- Beginning of Jn. 1 (writing exercise?): fol. 1v.&#xD;
- Ps. 110:10 (writing exercise?): fol. 2v. &#xD;
- Notes, including pen trial, partly in Amharic: fol. 2r.&#xD;
- Crude, very recent note in Tǝgrǝñña on the ownership of the Ms.: fol. 2v.&#xD;
- Crude notes in the upper margin: fols. 88r, 89r, 90v, 93r, 94r, etc.&#xD;
- Pen trials: fol. 135v.&#xD;
- Unfinished note (?): fol. 136v.</item>
